ecommendationservice-0", "recommendationservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "shippingservice-0", "shippingservice-1", "shippingservice-2"], "metric_name": ["cpu_usage", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "pod_cpu_usage", "request", "response", "rrt", "rrt_max"]}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["currencyservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "currencyservice-1", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["frontend-2", "cartservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "checkoutservice-1", "recommendationservice-0", "adservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-24T02:10:12Z and 2025-06-24T02:26:12Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-24 02:10:12+00:00 to 2025-06-24 02:26:12+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["currencyservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "currencyservice-1", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["frontend-2", "cartservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "checkoutservice-1", "recommendationservice-0", "adservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["cpu_usage", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "pod_cpu_usage", "request", "response", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "根据日志分析结果，没有检测到在2025-06-24T02:10:12Z到2025-06-24T02:26:12Z期间的错误日志。因此，当前阶段无法验证任何故障根因假设。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [],\n  \"hypotheses\": []\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "经过对调用链数据的分析，我们发现以下关键异常组件及其对应的延迟和故障情况：\n\n### 延迟异常分析\n\n1. **Redis高延迟**（Cart服务）\n   - Cart服务与Redis之间的连接在正常时段平均耗时约为 `<1573.06毫秒>`，异常时段增加至 `<12404.80毫秒>`，这表明异常时段有显著延迟。\n\n2. **Checkout服务**\n   - Checkout服务在异常期间较正常时段的延迟增加幅度较大，支付服务操作在异常时段耗时 `<40591.89毫秒>`，相较正常时段 `<13865.83毫秒>`，增加了近3倍。\n\n3. **Email服务**\n   - 发送订单确认邮件的耗时在异常时段明显增加，从正常的 `<753.57毫秒>` 增加到 `<2013.5毫秒>`。\n\n### 错误传递路径分析\n根因往往在于调用链中的最下游服务或者首次发生明显延迟的服务。依据调用链拓扑和数据：\n- Redis是Cart服务的关键存储组件，异常耗时增加显著，可能是主要的性能瓶颈。\n- Checkout服务的操作，尤其支付功能，耗时增加显著，需进一步排查其支付网关或支付后续操作异常。\n\n### JSON输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"redis->checkoutservice\", \"emailservice->checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常时段：1573.06ms，异常时段：12404.80ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常时段：13865.83ms，异常时段：40591.89ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常时段：753.57ms，异常时段：2013.5ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n结论是，Redis及Checkout服务出现在异常调用链的关键位置，且表现出显著的延迟翻倍和瓶颈行为，是导致异常的主要原因。根据拓扑，可能的故障源首先在于Redis，其次可能影响到Checkout及其他相关服务。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据从工具获取的数据，以下是关于异常事件的分析结果：\n\n### 检测到的关键异常指标\n- `rrt_max` (最大响应时间) 在多个服务中出现显著变化，包括 `cartservice`, `currencyservice`, `recommendationservice`, `shippingservice`, `emailservice`。\n- `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 在节点 `aiops-k8s-08` 和 `aiops-k8s-04` 上均显著下降。\n- `pod_cpu_usage` 对 `redis-cart-0` 的影响较小。\n- TiDB 相关的 `cpu_usage` 指标变化不显著。\n\n### 分析与假设验证\n根据故障模式识别优先级，节点资源故障被优先分析。对于节点 `aiops-k8s-08`，其可用内存显著下降，与多个 Pod 的关联如下：\n\n#### Pod 与 Node 的关联分析\n- **Pod**: `redis-cart-0` 在 `aiops-k8s-08` 上运行，但其 CPU 使用变化不显著，指向该 Pod 可能不是主因。\n- **其他影响服务及 Pod**: `frontend-2`, `cartservice-2`, `productcatalogservice-0`, `paymentservice-0` 均运行在 `aiops-k8s-08`，无明显单独异常表现，可能与节点整体内存情况相关。\n\n#### 重新评估节点和服务影响:\n- `aiops-k8s-08` 的内存可用性降低，结合 `node_filesystem_usage_rate` 未检测到异常，因此推测整体资源瓶颈可能是相关进程或硬件故障。\n- 服务响应时间的上升，尤其 `currencyservice`, `recommendationservice`, `shippingservice`, `emailservice`，其 `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 并没有显著变化指向 Pod 问题。\n\n### 输出结果\n结合以上分析，假设验证表明当前根因为节点 `aiops-k8s-08` 的内存可用性问题，可能影响多个服务的响应时间。Pod 级故障暂未发现有直接表征。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存可用性降低，影响多服务响应时间。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"数据期间节点内存 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 下降显著，服务响应时间 `rrt_max` 在多个服务上显著上升。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"虽然 `pod_cpu_usage` 有轻微变化，但不绝对显著，排除主要故障原因。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Pod CPU 变化轻微，主要影响仍与节点资源相关。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "current_hypothesis": "aiops-k8s-08 节点内存不足导致 Redis 高延迟，连锁影响多服务性能。"}
